lenders.name: acuity brands
lenders.occupational_info:
Proud to be Your Total Lighting Renovation Specialist
As the world's leading provider of lighting and controls, our reputation for customized lighting renovations may come as no surprise. We have delivered renovation solutions for over 10,000 facilities and we take great pride in our innovative products, service instincts and commitment to value.
You’ll Know Us By Our Brands
Our renovation solutions are enabled by the industry's strongest portfolio of lighting and control products, optimized for your application. So whether your solution involves retrofitting, relighting, replacement, redesign – or all of the above – you'll have access to the right energy-efficient products to meet your lighting and energy objectives.
Count on Superior Service
Acuity Brands Renovation is committed to serving the customer before, during and after the sale. With this in mind, we've assembled an extremely capable network of local lighting management contractors, many of whom are members of our EnergyLink program. The opportunity to collaborate with customers is our pleasure, and we strive to be a company that’s easy to do business with.
